description:
In this karaoke version of O the Deep, Deep Love of Jesus, we take a look at how God's love transforms our lives. From brokenhearted to free, this song is sure to touch your heart!
If you're looking for a fun and easy way to enjoy worship music, then check out this karaoke version of O the Deep, Deep Love of Jesus. With lyrics that talk about how God's love transforms our lives, this song is sure to touch your heart!

Author: S. Trevor Francis
Music performed by C Lalhmuaka, 3 Sisters Youtube Production.
